Abstract = {{The objective of this study is to study the influence of de-inking paper
   sludge (DPS) and sewage sludge (SL) mixtures addition at different rates
   (2, 4 and 8\%) in two soils. Incubation experiments were performed
   during 60 days and the influence of treatments in physical soil
   properties was determined by soil porosity and stability of aggregates.
   Differential thermal analysis (DTA) of amended soils after incubation
